sources.description: SUBSCRIBE A dangerous cougar is the central element in this tale of a young man who returns to his mother's birthplace, which happens to be a small valley in draught-wrecked southern Utah. The youngster finds himself involved in a feud between two men hoping to collect the bounty on the killer cat.
